cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with the use of deep learning techniques for road segmentation in SAR satellite images. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also involves the use of machine learning algorithms (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) for image segmentation. The use of SAR satellite images also involves the processing of remote sensing data (cs.GR). Finally, the paper involves the evaluation of different models, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
